text: Rahul Buddhi (born 20 September 1997) is an Indian cricketer. He made his first-class debut on 19 January 2020, for Hyderabad in the 2019–20 Ranji Trophy. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Indian cricketers Category:Hyderabad cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
